description:
This popup application allows to dial full telephone number by inputing only last extension digits:
- Create, edit phone number's filters,
- Enter the prefix of the phone filter,
- Select the number of digits for the extension,
- Select the key digit to recognize the extension,
- The model of dialed phone number is displayed,
- Allow to dial a full phone number,
- Go to the Dial dashboard and enter the extension number.

Changelog:
1.1.2
- Manage multiple phone filters,
- Display the company called,
- Allow to dial full phone number,

1.0.1
- NEW >>> TouchPad version in 100% Enyo framework,
- NEW >>> Phone version with Enyo from Maps,
- English, French, German and Spanish users,
- Last calls stack and '+' key,

1.0.0
- first application (App Hack),
- HP Pre 3 version in 100% Enyo,
